data.description: This beautiful Colonial has an updated kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless appliances, lots of storage and beautiful wood flooring throughout. New programmable water heater allows you to control the water temperature right from your phone. The primary bedroom has an enlarged primary bath with walk in closet. Enjoy your days basking in the sunlight coming through the windows of the sunroom or taking in the surroundings out on the screened in porch. All of this within minutes of Olde Town, Portsmouth Naval Hospital, and Norfolk Naval Shipyard.
